  "instructions": [
    "Heat a pan over medium-high heat. Add turmeric and salt to the pan, cooking until fragrant.",
    "Add diced pineapple, finely chopped onion, minced garlic, and sliced bell pepper into the pan. Stir-fry for about 3 minutes.",
    "Reduce heat to low-medium and add sugarcane syrup and coconut milk. Stir constantly for another 2-3 minutes or until desired consistency is achieved.",
    "Fold in fresh cilantro before serving hot."
